main event: On 19 October 1962, a rectangular object was observed hovering in Eutaw, Alabama for approximately 22 minutes.
interesting points: The object was described as being 50-60 feet long and 8-12 feet high, The object displayed a mass of blinking lights and produced no sound, It appeared to be spinning steadily during the observation, The object climbed rapidly and disappeared at dawn, Initial conclusions considered it as a balloon or possibly an aircraft.
